<plot>This was a 30 minute weekday childrens' show which aired on WPIX Channel 11 from 1972 to 1984, and was at some point syndicated nationally. The show concerned two women, Carol and Paula, who sat around the Magic Garden, singing, telling jokes, acting out stories, and talking with puppets Sherlock (a squirrel) and Flapper (a bird).</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573392</url></doc>
